{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/cabinet-office/about/media-enquiries","content_id":"5f560b7a-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Cabinet Office press office only deals with enquiries from the media.</p>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please use the public correspondence <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/contact-the-cabinet-office\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact form</a>.</p>\n\n<p>If you are a journalist with a press enquiry or interview request, please email our <a href=\"mailto:pressoffice@cabinetoffice.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">press office</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>Please note, if you have a media query concerning the Prime Minister or media access to Downing Street - please call the press office for No10 Downing Street.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Change of phone number","public_timestamp":"2022-10-03T11:03:44Z"},{"note":"Additional contact details for the UK Presidency of the G7 and the UK Presidency of the COP26 UN Climate Change Conference.","public_timestamp":"2021-03-30T14:30:03Z"},{"note":"The public information line number has been removed as it is no longer in use.","public_timestamp":"2019-06-12T09:22:27Z"},{"note":"Changed press office email to pressoffice@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","public_timestamp":"2019-06-11T14:44:12Z"},{"note":"Added new press officer on.","public_timestamp":"2018-01-04T13:26:49Z"},{"note":"New Head of News added","public_timestamp":"2017-12-05T13:10:43Z"},{"note":"Updated press officers.","public_timestamp":"2017-10-30T12:21:30Z"},{"note":"Updated role titles","public_timestamp":"2017-06-13T16:04:12Z"},{"note":"Updated roles and duties","public_timestamp":"2017-06-13T13:30:39Z"},{"note":"updated contacts","public_timestamp":"2015-11-26T15:09:34Z"},{"note":"Updated contact information.","public_timestamp":"2015-07-30T14:31:15Z"},{"note":"First published.","pu